short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension saves the current tabs prfile and one can open the saved tab profile for later use.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With this extension you can save your opened tabs in the current window for future use. It can be used to create different groups of tabs on different subjects , which can be reopened in different devices you are logged in.

Features: 
1. Ability to save opened tabs with unique name and reopening them in another window when needed.
2. Ability to open the tabs saved in any profile.
3. Ability to delete tabs from any profile.
